smodule:module_composition_127 dcterms:title "UniProt entries use ChEBI in the following annotations: Ligands, Cofactors and Enzymatic Activity. This query shows how these can all be retrieved in one go, to make a UniProt to ChEBI mapping. The example query is made smaller by retrieving only human entries in Swiss-Prot.".
smodule:module_composition_127 rdfs:comment "UniProt entries use ChEBI in the following annotations: Ligands, Cofactors and Enzymatic Activity. This query shows how these can all be retrieved in one go, to make a UniProt to ChEBI mapping. The example query is made smaller by retrieving only human entries in Swiss-Prot.".
smodule:module_composition_127 dcterms:subject "ChEBI", "catalytic activity", "cofactor", "enzyme", "ligand".

